1
00:00:00,530 --> 00:00:03,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is Kobe!</font>

2
00:00:03,230 --> 00:00:05,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's so nice!</font>

3
00:00:05,170 --> 00:00:07,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh man, my first time 
in Kansai! I'm pumped!</font>

4
00:00:07,630 --> 00:00:10,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right. Next stop, my house, 'kay?</font>

5
00:00:11,940 --> 00:00:12,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's with those faces?</font>

6
00:00:12,990 --> 00:00:15,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Obviously, we're gonna see the sights!</font>

7
00:00:15,540 --> 00:00:17,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What, seriously? Isn't it hot?</font>

8
00:00:17,240 --> 00:00:19,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you think, Yoi-chan?!</font>

9
00:00:20,100 --> 00:00:22,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll go along with 
whatever you guys decide.</font>

10
00:00:22,580 --> 00:00:25,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right! Sightseeing it is, then!</font>

11
00:00:25,730 --> 00:00:27,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yay!</font>

12
00:01:58,010 --> 00:01:59,510
<font size="20">{\an8}<b><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#837a61">Hyogo</font></font></b></font>

13
00:01:58,010 --> 00:01:59,510
<font size="20">{\an8}<b><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#81695d">Nankinmachi</font></font></b></font>

14
00:02:00,620 --> 00:02:02,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That looks so good!</font>

15
00:02:02,290 --> 00:02:04,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's a panda one, too! So cute!</font>

16
00:02:04,960 --> 00:02:06,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wanna get it?</font>

17
00:02:06,080 --> 00:02:08,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll pass. I'll wait here.</font>

18
00:02:08,690 --> 00:02:10,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not hungry either, so I'll wait, too.</font>

19
00:02:11,260 --> 00:02:13,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, then we'll be back in a bit.</font>

20
00:02:13,970 --> 00:02:17,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}I wonder what's in the panda one?</font>

21
00:02:15,900 --> 00:02:17,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're sure full of energy.</font>

22
00:02:18,180 --> 00:02:22,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Man, it sure is hot.</font>

23
00:02:22,810 --> 00:02:24,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you all right?</font>

24
00:02:24,240 --> 00:02:27,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I naturally run hot, 
so I can't stand this weather.</font>

25
00:02:28,260 --> 00:02:29,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Oh...</i></font>

26
00:02:31,940 --> 00:02:35,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you'd like, you can 
join me under the parasol?</font>

27
00:02:35,320 --> 00:02:36,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Does that keep you cool?</font>

28
00:02:37,370 --> 00:02:38,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, it's cool.</font>

29
00:02:39,310 --> 00:02:40,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh.</font>

30
00:02:50,990 --> 00:02:53,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, you're right.</font>

31
00:02:53,980 --> 00:02:55,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a bit cooler.</font>

32
00:02:57,150 --> 00:03:00,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Th-This doesn't make it cooler!</i></font>

33
00:03:01,250 --> 00:03:02,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is he doing this on purpose?</i></font>

34
00:03:02,860 --> 00:03:05,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm amazed that you even 
brought your parasol with you.</font>

35
00:03:06,440 --> 00:03:10,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When I stand in the sun too long,
my skin turns bright red.</font>

36
00:03:10,650 --> 00:03:13,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You do have fair skin, Yoi-chan.</font>

37
00:03:14,010 --> 00:03:16,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you sure you're okay 
staying behind, Senpai?</font>

38
00:03:17,090 --> 00:03:19,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We came all the way to Chinatown...</font>

39
00:03:22,220 --> 00:03:22,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

40
00:03:23,870 --> 00:03:27,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't care what we do, 
as long as I get to be with you.</font>

41
00:03:28,350 --> 00:03:29,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And, well...</font>

42
00:03:29,770 --> 00:03:31,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to flirt with you more.</font>

43
00:03:37,780 --> 00:03:39,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey!</font>

44
00:03:39,610 --> 00:03:41,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We went and bought it!</font>

45
00:03:41,790 --> 00:03:43,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? What's up?</font>

46
00:03:43,900 --> 00:03:44,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nothing.</font>

47
00:03:46,520 --> 00:03:48,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! That's mine!</font>

48
00:03:48,510 --> 00:03:49,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I feel like...</i></font>

49
00:03:50,250 --> 00:03:53,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Senpai is a little different 
from his usual self today.</i></font>

50
00:03:55,290 --> 00:03:57,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The clothes I bought and 
the earrings, too...</i></font>

51
00:03:58,110 --> 00:03:59,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Maybe I should have worn them.</i></font>

52
00:04:01,070 --> 00:04:02,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Maybe...</i></font>

53
00:04:02,410 --> 00:04:04,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The two of us should have 
just come on our own.</i></font>

54
00:04:07,020 --> 00:04:07,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

55
00:04:11,240 --> 00:04:13,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anyway, just have a seat wherever.</font>

56
00:04:13,960 --> 00:04:17,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">W-Wow! This is insane!</font>

57
00:04:15,930 --> 00:04:18,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Oh, man, amazing! Thanks for having me.</font>

58
00:04:17,450 --> 00:04:19,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is your boyfriend's family an oil tycoon?</font>

59
00:04:18,670 --> 00:04:21,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Your house is amazing, but 
this is really something, too.</font>

60
00:04:19,660 --> 00:04:21,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I don't think so.</font>

61
00:04:22,020 --> 00:04:23,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is anyone hungry?</font>

62
00:04:23,550 --> 00:04:25,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm about to order. 
What do you guys want?</font>

63
00:04:25,550 --> 00:04:26,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm hungry!</font>

64
00:04:26,460 --> 00:04:27,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Since we have the chance,</font>

65
00:04:27,530 --> 00:04:29,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd like to watch something 
while we eat pizza and stuff!</font>

66
00:04:34,710 --> 00:04:36,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A slingshot isn't going to cut it!</font>

67
00:04:36,810 --> 00:04:38,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Millie, please wake up!</font>

68
00:04:38,470 --> 00:04:39,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's gonna happen?!</font>

69
00:04:39,720 --> 00:04:41,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, you want me to spoil it?</font>

70
00:04:41,320 --> 00:04:42,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't you dare!</font>

71
00:04:42,080 --> 00:04:43,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone, run away!</font>

72
00:04:45,170 --> 00:04:46,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Does anyone want something to drink?</font>

73
00:04:47,040 --> 00:04:48,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I'm good.</font>

74
00:04:48,710 --> 00:04:49,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Me, too.</font>

75
00:04:49,620 --> 00:04:50,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Me, too.</font>

76
00:04:50,330 --> 00:04:52,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Me, too. Thanks.</font>

77
00:04:52,340 --> 00:04:52,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yoi-chan?</font>

78
00:04:53,220 --> 00:04:54,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I could get it my—</font>

79
00:04:54,780 --> 00:04:56,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's all right, I'll get it for you.</font>

80
00:04:57,860 --> 00:04:59,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tea okay?</font>

81
00:04:59,090 --> 00:05:00,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, sorry to trouble you.</font>

82
00:05:03,610 --> 00:05:04,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Senpai...</i></font>

83
00:05:05,770 --> 00:05:09,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He sort of mentioned how he keeps 
the location of his house a secret.</i></font>

84
00:05:11,660 --> 00:05:16,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Was it really okay for me to ask him 
to bring my friends here too?</i></font>

85
00:05:19,620 --> 00:05:23,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, are we really gonna end up 
watching this til season two?</font>

86
00:05:26,460 --> 00:05:28,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wouldn't it be faster if I just
spoiled it for you all?</font>

87
00:05:28,560 --> 00:05:31,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like I said, don't you dare!</font>

88
00:05:31,800 --> 00:05:34,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! They're flirting!</font>

89
00:05:34,320 --> 00:05:35,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're so loud.</font>

90
00:05:35,430 --> 00:05:37,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's shameless, <i>shameless</i> I say!</font>

91
00:05:37,640 --> 00:05:39,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm just sitting next to her.</font>

92
00:05:39,860 --> 00:05:41,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think I'm doing great
at containing myself.</font>

93
00:05:41,510 --> 00:05:43,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anyway, look, Millie's in trouble.</font>

94
00:05:43,700 --> 00:05:44,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

95
00:05:44,910 --> 00:05:48,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Ah! Why is Millie the 
only one with powers?!</font>

96
00:05:44,910 --> 00:05:46,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Well, yeah...</i></font>

97
00:05:47,290 --> 00:05:48,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's true...</i></font>

98
00:05:48,260 --> 00:05:50,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He is just sitting next to me, but...</i></font>

99
00:05:50,930 --> 00:05:51,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey.</font>

100
00:05:52,870 --> 00:05:54,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?! Oh, yes?</font>

101
00:05:58,100 --> 00:05:58,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I...</font>

102
00:06:01,900 --> 00:06:04,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">want to hang out tonight.
 Just the two of us.</font>

103
00:06:11,750 --> 00:06:12,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

104
00:06:17,090 --> 00:06:19,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I said, "Okay," without giving 
it much thought, but...</i></font>

105
00:06:20,220 --> 00:06:22,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It'll be all right... Right?</i></font>

106
00:06:22,840 --> 00:06:24,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And, well...
I want to flirt with you more.</i></font>

107
00:06:25,900 --> 00:06:28,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>N-No, that can't be it!</i></font>

108
00:06:29,020 --> 00:06:30,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Besides...</i></font>

109
00:06:30,360 --> 00:06:33,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't care what we do, 
as long as I get to be with you.</font>

110
00:06:34,120 --> 00:06:36,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Just... how do I put it...</i></font>

111
00:06:39,520 --> 00:06:39,620
<font size="20">{\an8}<b><font size="22"><font color="#51504e">You have a new message.</font></font></b></font>

