124
00:06:51,780 --> 00:06:55,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yes... I'm still awake.</font>

125
00:06:57,620 --> 00:06:58,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm.</font>

126
00:07:06,910 --> 00:07:08,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Excuse me.</font>

127
00:07:10,210 --> 00:07:13,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Senpai... just got out of the bath.</i></font>

128
00:07:14,050 --> 00:07:15,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How about the others?</font>

129
00:07:16,160 --> 00:07:18,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, they're already asleep.</font>

130
00:07:18,550 --> 00:07:20,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How about your friends, Senpai?</font>

131
00:07:20,510 --> 00:07:23,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kuwa's already asleep, but Sentaro 
is playing games in the room.</font>

132
00:07:24,860 --> 00:07:28,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I told him I was going to 
shower and forced my way out.</font>

133
00:07:31,340 --> 00:07:36,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, Senpai, did you have fun today?</font>

134
00:07:36,350 --> 00:07:37,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Why d'you ask?</font>

135
00:07:38,950 --> 00:07:42,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, you let my friends 
come along because I asked.</font>

136
00:07:42,560 --> 00:07:48,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But maybe our first summer break together
should have been just us, like you said.</font>

137
00:07:48,830 --> 00:07:49,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You taking this too seriously?</font>

138
00:07:49,970 --> 00:07:50,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

139
00:07:52,060 --> 00:07:53,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't have to worry 
about things like that.</font>

140
00:07:53,980 --> 00:07:57,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We won't get many chances like this,
 and it's been pretty fun.</font>

141
00:07:57,960 --> 00:08:00,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's kinda like a school trip, y'know?</font>

142
00:08:02,520 --> 00:08:05,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Oh... I get it.</i></font>

143
00:08:05,670 --> 00:08:10,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We won't be going on our school trip 
or graduating in the same year...</i></font>

144
00:08:11,560 --> 00:08:12,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I see.</i></font>

145
00:08:13,340 --> 00:08:16,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But, well, to be honest,
if it was just the two of us,</font>

146
00:08:16,140 --> 00:08:17,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">we could've flirted a bit more.</font>

147
00:08:19,160 --> 00:08:22,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm telling you right now,
there will be <i>none</i> of that today.</font>

148
00:08:22,360 --> 00:08:25,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even holding hands?
Not even a hug? Are you serious?!</font>

149
00:08:25,110 --> 00:08:25,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

150
00:08:26,850 --> 00:08:28,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're... serious...</font>

151
00:08:30,110 --> 00:08:34,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, don't you think you're a little 
excessive with physical contact, Senpai?</font>

152
00:08:35,510 --> 00:08:36,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In various ways...</font>

153
00:08:37,910 --> 00:08:39,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's because.</font>

154
00:08:42,340 --> 00:08:45,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you like someone, isn't it
 normal to want to touch them?</font>

155
00:08:46,660 --> 00:08:47,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Am I wrong?</font>

156
00:08:47,940 --> 00:08:49,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Oh, gosh!</i></font>

157
00:08:49,210 --> 00:08:51,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I won't deny that, but...</font>

158
00:08:51,940 --> 00:08:56,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">are you always like this 
when you date a girl?</font>

159
00:08:58,920 --> 00:08:59,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

160
00:09:02,120 --> 00:09:03,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Must have been my imagination.</font>

161
00:09:03,990 --> 00:09:04,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh!</font>

162
00:09:04,640 --> 00:09:06,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's pizza left over.</font>

163
00:09:07,470 --> 00:09:09,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why do we have to hide?!</font>

164
00:09:09,820 --> 00:09:12,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">'Cause it'll be a pain
 if he goes off again.</font>

165
00:09:12,610 --> 00:09:16,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But it doesn't mean he had to 
go right from that to this...</i></font>

166
00:09:16,230 --> 00:09:18,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know any other way.</font>

167
00:09:20,770 --> 00:09:26,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Up until now... I thought dating just 
meant sticking together and making out.</font>

168
00:09:27,370 --> 00:09:29,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought that's what it 
meant to be in love.</font>

169
00:09:31,240 --> 00:09:32,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But...</font>

170
00:09:33,400 --> 00:09:35,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When it comes to you, Yoi-chan,</font>

171
00:09:35,290 --> 00:09:37,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">as much as I want you and 
want to get to know you more...</font>

172
00:09:38,050 --> 00:09:38,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">at the same time...</font>

173
00:09:39,340 --> 00:09:41,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I also want to cherish you.</font>

174
00:09:41,540 --> 00:09:43,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have these conflicting feelings.</font>

175
00:09:44,760 --> 00:09:45,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Still...</font>

176
00:09:45,750 --> 00:09:49,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't know any other way to express 
my feelings other than by "touching,"</font>

177
00:09:49,830 --> 00:09:52,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so sometimes I don't know what to do.</font>

178
00:09:53,010 --> 00:09:53,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I sorta...</font>

179
00:09:56,460 --> 00:09:58,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">don't even know what I'm saying anymore.</font>

180
00:09:59,670 --> 00:10:03,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Wh-Who even is this awkward person?</i></font>

181
00:10:03,420 --> 00:10:06,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't care what we do, 
as long as I get to be with you.</font>

182
00:10:07,090 --> 00:10:10,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's the same feeling as 
when I heard those words...</i></font>

183
00:10:10,220 --> 00:10:13,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This feeling that bubbles 
up inside my heart...</i></font>

184
00:10:13,560 --> 00:10:16,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Just what do you call this feeling?</i></font>

185
00:10:28,520 --> 00:10:30,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mi amore!</font>

186
00:10:36,340 --> 00:10:37,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um...</font>

187
00:10:38,100 --> 00:10:39,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you'd like...</font>

188
00:10:40,140 --> 00:10:43,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Before we leave tomorrow, 
we could go someplace together.</font>

189
00:10:44,330 --> 00:10:47,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">L-Like... on a date.</font>

190
00:10:51,010 --> 00:10:51,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure.</font>

191
00:10:52,730 --> 00:10:53,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's do it.</font>

192
00:10:56,100 --> 00:10:59,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">W-Well then, I guess we 
should head to bed.</font>

193
00:10:59,860 --> 00:11:00,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm.</font>

194
00:11:00,990 --> 00:11:03,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For tomorrow... Is ten too early?</font>

195
00:11:03,870 --> 00:11:04,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No.</font>

196
00:11:04,970 --> 00:11:07,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then let's meet in the living room at ten.</font>

197
00:11:07,610 --> 00:11:08,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm.</font>

198
00:11:09,340 --> 00:11:11,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">G-Good night.</font>

199
00:11:23,740 --> 00:11:24,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's up?</font>

200
00:11:25,820 --> 00:11:26,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A hug.</font>

201
00:11:27,700 --> 00:11:29,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">May I please...</font>

202
00:11:29,910 --> 00:11:31,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">have a goodnight hug?</font>

203
00:11:33,130 --> 00:11:34,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey...</font>

204
00:11:34,710 --> 00:11:36,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You messing with me?</font>

205
00:11:37,380 --> 00:11:39,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Besides, you're the one 
who said it, didn't you?</font>

206
00:11:39,520 --> 00:11:40,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sayin' there'd be none of that.</font>

207
00:11:41,240 --> 00:11:42,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I know.</font>

208
00:11:43,680 --> 00:11:48,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I feel like I kinda understand 
what you were saying.</font>

209
00:11:51,510 --> 00:11:52,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to cherish you...</font>

210
00:11:53,350 --> 00:11:54,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I want to touch you.</font>

211
00:11:55,880 --> 00:11:59,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's why, right now,
I want to touch you, Senpai.</font>

212
00:12:06,120 --> 00:12:07,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're killin' me.</font>

213
00:12:08,590 --> 00:12:09,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know.</font>

214
00:12:26,410 --> 00:12:28,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good night.</font>

215
00:12:38,660 --> 00:12:41,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Oh, man, what is this?</i></font>

216
00:12:41,150 --> 00:12:43,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What am I... What am I even doing?!</i></font>

217
00:12:44,430 --> 00:12:45,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can't stay calm...</i></font>

218
00:12:46,460 --> 00:12:48,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Just thinking about it is embarrassing...</i></font>

219
00:12:48,870 --> 00:12:49,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But still...</i></font>

220
00:12:50,370 --> 00:12:53,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Senpai's body temperature... 
The feel of his arms...</i></font>

221
00:12:53,760 --> 00:12:56,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The smell of his shampoo, his breathing...</i></font>

222
00:12:57,010 --> 00:12:59,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>All of it, all of it, all of it,</i></font>

223
00:12:59,410 --> 00:13:02,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>is ruminating in my brain.</i></font>

224
00:13:02,500 --> 00:13:05,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm losing myself.</i></font>

225
00:13:08,760 --> 00:13:11,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, did you just get out of the bath?</font>

226
00:13:11,520 --> 00:13:14,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gotta say, that was awfully long.</font>

227
00:13:14,630 --> 00:13:16,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who are you, Shizuka-chan?</font>

228
00:13:18,330 --> 00:13:19,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nah.</font>

229
00:13:20,190 --> 00:13:21,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come again?</font>

230
00:13:24,200 --> 00:13:25,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Just what do you...</i></font>

231
00:13:26,460 --> 00:13:29,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>call this feeling?</i></font>

232
00:13:38,170 --> 00:13:41,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-Wha, what? What? What's wrong?!</font>

233
00:13:41,160 --> 00:13:42,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}My glasses, glasses...</font>

234
00:13:41,710 --> 00:13:42,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um...</font>

235
00:13:44,040 --> 00:13:47,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Actually, I have something I need 
to talk to you guys about.</font>

236
00:13:54,220 --> 00:13:55,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um!</font>

237
00:13:57,350 --> 00:13:59,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry for being late.</font>

238
00:14:00,520 --> 00:14:03,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It took a bit longer 
than I thought, and...</font>

239
00:14:07,650 --> 00:14:10,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, Yoi-chan, you seem a 
bit sparkly today, yeah?</font>

240
00:14:11,580 --> 00:14:13,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What do you mean by that?!</font>

241
00:14:13,900 --> 00:14:16,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, how should I put it...</font>

242
00:14:16,820 --> 00:14:19,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nah, actually never mind. 
Don't worry about it.</font>

243
00:14:21,010 --> 00:14:23,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anyway, let's go before it gets hot.</font>

244
00:14:24,840 --> 00:14:29,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I actually had Nobara and Kotobuki 
do a few things for me, but...</i></font>

245
00:14:29,420 --> 00:14:33,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I wanted a little more of
 a reaction... I guess.</i></font>

246
00:14:33,360 --> 00:14:35,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did Ichi leave already?</font>

247
00:14:35,630 --> 00:14:36,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Probably.</font>

248
00:14:37,290 --> 00:14:39,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn it, they're coming!</font>

249
00:14:39,070 --> 00:14:39,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go!</font>

250
00:14:42,850 --> 00:14:45,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't want them to see 
how you look today.</font>

251
00:14:50,580 --> 00:14:51,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I suppose...</font>

252
00:14:52,910 --> 00:14:54,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that I'll take that as a compliment.</font>

253
00:14:55,580 --> 00:14:56,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can.</font>

254
00:14:59,310 --> 00:15:00,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's almost like he's shining.</i></font>

255
00:15:01,210 --> 00:15:02,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's making me dizzy.</i></font>

256
00:15:09,770 --> 00:15:11,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow!</font>

257
00:15:12,430 --> 00:15:14,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What a beautiful aquarium.</font>

258
00:15:14,950 --> 00:15:17,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I did a little research last night.</font>

259
00:15:18,600 --> 00:15:20,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, hey.</font>

260
00:15:21,730 --> 00:15:22,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it?</font>

261
00:15:23,210 --> 00:15:25,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I would like to hold your hand.</font>

262
00:15:25,990 --> 00:15:26,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um!</font>

263
00:15:27,780 --> 00:15:28,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes!</font>

264
00:15:31,660 --> 00:15:33,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">One vote... in favor.</font>

265
00:15:53,590 --> 00:15:55,050
<font size="20">{\an8}<b><font color="#706386">Koi Food</font></b></font>

266
00:16:14,910 --> 00:16:16,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here.</font>

267
00:16:18,820 --> 00:16:20,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's good, so...</font>

268
00:16:26,890 --> 00:16:28,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, this is cute.</font>

269
00:16:29,810 --> 00:16:31,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A gift for your friends?</font>

270
00:16:31,210 --> 00:16:32,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, it's for my big sis.</font>

271
00:16:32,370 --> 00:16:34,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What, you have a big sis?</font>

272
00:16:32,900 --> 00:16:35,840
<font size="20">{\an8}<font face="Comic Sans MS"><b><font size="8"><font color="#a5946c">Big Sister</font></font></b></font></font>

273
00:16:34,660 --> 00:16:35,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, yes.</font>

274
00:16:36,180 --> 00:16:37,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you want to see a pic?</font>

275
00:16:37,590 --> 00:16:40,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh, you guys don't look much alike.</font>

276
00:16:40,840 --> 00:16:42,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I get that a lot.</font>

277
00:16:43,230 --> 00:16:44,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Unlike me...</font>

278
00:16:45,580 --> 00:16:50,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My big sister looks very girly, 
so she's always been popular.</font>

279
00:16:50,360 --> 00:16:51,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh-huh...</font>

280
00:16:52,590 --> 00:16:55,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">During my first year of junior high,</font>

281
00:16:55,170 --> 00:16:57,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">there was a boy I had a 
little crush on and...</font>

282
00:16:58,110 --> 00:17:01,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, I wonder if Takiguchi 
has a crush on you.</font>

283
00:17:01,030 --> 00:17:03,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are ya gonna do if 
she confesses to you?</font>

284
00:17:03,010 --> 00:17:04,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?!</font>

285
00:17:04,160 --> 00:17:07,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's no way I can date a 
girl who's taller than me.</font>

286
00:17:07,990 --> 00:17:11,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Would've been better if it was 
her big sis instead.</font>

287
00:17:11,250 --> 00:17:12,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

288
00:17:12,760 --> 00:17:14,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where does he live?</font>

289
00:17:14,510 --> 00:17:15,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's his high school?</font>

290
00:17:15,690 --> 00:17:16,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Middle school?</font>

291
00:17:15,880 --> 00:17:17,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}P-Please stop.</font>

292
00:17:16,400 --> 00:17:16,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Elementary?</font>

293
00:17:16,970 --> 00:17:18,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What ward, what block, 
what building, what number?</font>

294
00:17:17,530 --> 00:17:18,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}It's all in the past.</font>

295
00:17:18,800 --> 00:17:20,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I'm <i>gonna</i> find out.</font>

296
00:17:20,610 --> 00:17:21,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Still...</font>

297
00:17:21,850 --> 00:17:25,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think that's when I sort of started 
to have trouble talking to guys...</font>

298
00:17:27,050 --> 00:17:31,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, but I do love my big sis, so I'm 
honestly happy when she gets praised.</font>

299
00:17:32,300 --> 00:17:33,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see now.</font>

300
00:17:34,300 --> 00:17:37,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, that's the cause of 
your low self-esteem.</font>

301
00:17:38,830 --> 00:17:41,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can you show me your sis one more time?</font>

302
00:17:41,610 --> 00:17:42,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, sure.</font>

303
00:17:44,950 --> 00:17:46,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, I like you better.</font>

304
00:17:47,270 --> 00:17:50,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What about me?</font>

305
00:17:50,130 --> 00:17:52,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm? Well, your face?</font>

306
00:17:52,950 --> 00:17:54,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I shouldn't have asked.</i></font>

307
00:17:55,330 --> 00:17:57,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you have any siblings, Senpai?</font>

308
00:17:57,830 --> 00:17:59,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I do. One older brother.</font>

309
00:17:59,820 --> 00:18:00,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh.</font>

310
00:18:01,090 --> 00:18:02,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's a fine young man.</font>

311
00:18:02,900 --> 00:18:05,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A steady, honest, upstanding citizen.</font>

312
00:18:05,070 --> 00:18:08,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? I kind of... can't picture that.</font>

313
00:18:08,920 --> 00:18:11,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He <i>is</i> the total opposite of me.</font>

314
00:18:11,460 --> 00:18:13,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dunno where he is or what 
he's doing right now.</font>

315
00:18:14,870 --> 00:18:16,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Does that mean...</font>

316
00:18:16,620 --> 00:18:19,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Some things happened
between him and his ex.</font>

317
00:18:19,630 --> 00:18:21,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He fought with our parents, too.</font>

318
00:18:21,160 --> 00:18:22,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Haven't heard from him since.</font>

319
00:18:25,250 --> 00:18:25,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well...</font>

320
00:18:27,430 --> 00:18:29,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Life's full of surprises, yeah?</font>

321
00:18:34,150 --> 00:18:39,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He made it sound like nothing, but 
that's not a common situation at all.</i></font>

322
00:18:42,850 --> 00:18:48,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Why was he talking about his own family
 like it was someone else's problem?</i></font>

323
00:19:01,000 --> 00:19:02,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yoi-chan!</font>

324
00:19:02,080 --> 00:19:02,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See ya.</font>

325
00:19:04,910 --> 00:19:06,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You should've said something.</font>

326
00:19:08,120 --> 00:19:10,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it? What's wrong?</font>

327
00:19:11,250 --> 00:19:13,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those people you were with just now...</font>

328
00:19:13,610 --> 00:19:16,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I just picked up a 
cellphone they dropped.</font>

329
00:19:17,260 --> 00:19:18,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh-huh...</font>

330
00:19:21,740 --> 00:19:23,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh, could it be that...</font>

331
00:19:23,430 --> 00:19:24,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">you're jealous?</font>

332
00:19:25,340 --> 00:19:27,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-It's nothing like that!</font>

333
00:19:28,060 --> 00:19:29,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm heading out.</font>

334
00:19:29,630 --> 00:19:33,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Yoi-san, I was just kiddin'!</font>

335
00:19:34,360 --> 00:19:38,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Oh... Why am I always like this?</i></font>

336
00:19:38,280 --> 00:19:39,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whoa, amazing.</font>

337
00:19:40,970 --> 00:19:41,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right?</font>

338
00:19:42,280 --> 00:19:43,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

339
00:19:43,750 --> 00:19:46,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Still sulking?</font>

340
00:19:46,500 --> 00:19:47,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I am certainly—</font>

341
00:19:47,630 --> 00:19:49,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">not... sulking.</font>

342
00:19:50,190 --> 00:19:51,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really. It's just...</font>

343
00:19:52,670 --> 00:19:54,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm disgusted with myself.</font>

344
00:19:55,330 --> 00:19:56,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because...</font>

345
00:19:57,720 --> 00:20:01,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We were just having a serious 
conversation about your family,</font>

346
00:20:01,110 --> 00:20:03,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but then seeing you with other girls 
quickly made me lose my confidence,</font>

347
00:20:03,860 --> 00:20:06,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and on top of that, I became 
completely preoccupied with myself,</font>

348
00:20:05,640 --> 00:20:08,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Huh, wordy much?</font>

349
00:20:06,540 --> 00:20:09,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and as if that wasn't enough, I ended 
up making you have to cheer me up...</font>

350
00:20:09,560 --> 00:20:12,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I should have just admitted I was jealous.</font>

351
00:20:13,210 --> 00:20:16,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But instead, I ended up thinking
 those girls would suit you better</font>

352
00:20:16,890 --> 00:20:21,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">than someone who's putting in all her
 effort just to wear a dress for once.</font>

353
00:20:22,430 --> 00:20:23,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He was right.</i></font>

354
00:20:23,870 --> 00:20:28,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I really do have low self-esteem, don't I?</i></font>

355
00:20:28,860 --> 00:20:29,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yoi-chan...</font>

356
00:20:30,700 --> 00:20:32,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y'know how you don't look
at me as the Prince?</font>

357
00:20:33,960 --> 00:20:37,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've treated me as one of 
the guys right from the get-go.</font>

358
00:20:38,490 --> 00:20:41,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, maybe you just 
didn't like me at first...</font>

359
00:20:42,940 --> 00:20:47,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But... I feel like I can be myself 
when I'm with you, Yoi-chan.</font>

360
00:20:48,310 --> 00:20:50,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Laughing at stupid things.</font>

361
00:20:50,360 --> 00:20:52,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Holding hands while we walk.</font>

362
00:20:52,680 --> 00:20:57,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eating gyoza, eating dango, and 
talking side-by-side at night.</font>

363
00:20:57,960 --> 00:21:00,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seriously, just being with you is so fun.</font>

364
00:21:00,500 --> 00:21:03,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When I saw my bro broken, 
I honestly thought</font>

365
00:21:03,620 --> 00:21:05,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"He's so lame for feeling broken 
over something silly like love."</font>

366
00:21:06,460 --> 00:21:10,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But now, I'm thinking that 
love is pretty cool.</font>

367
00:21:11,560 --> 00:21:14,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Talk about your teenage cliché, right?</font>

368
00:21:15,210 --> 00:21:22,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I never thought I'd ever dress like this 
for someone and go on a date, either.</i></font>

369
00:21:23,220 --> 00:21:24,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um...</font>

370
00:21:24,410 --> 00:21:25,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I chose these earrings,</font>

371
00:21:26,050 --> 00:21:30,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">because I thought they looked similar 
to yours and we could match.</font>

372
00:21:30,610 --> 00:21:32,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought that might be the case.</font>

373
00:21:49,710 --> 00:21:51,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We should head back soon.</font>

374
00:21:52,940 --> 00:21:53,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I...</i></font>

375
00:21:54,580 --> 00:21:59,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I think I'm going to end up 
loving him more and more.</i></font>

376
00:22:07,570 --> 00:22:09,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You could have...</i></font>

377
00:22:12,330 --> 00:22:13,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>kissed me, y'know.</i></font>

378
00:22:13,200 --> 00:22:15,790
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="18"><font color="#2f2a58"><b><font face="Comic Sans MS">A Goodnight Hug</font></b></font></font></font>

